words of good cheer

1036
01:18:31,073 --> 01:18:33,850
that I can send in to Forbin
via Dr. Markham?

1037
01:18:33,899 --> 01:18:37,400
Tell him we're trying to establish
an international pool of information.

1038
01:18:37,470 --> 01:18:40,030
A courier system has to be set up
between Washington...

1039
01:18:40,060 --> 01:18:41,500
and Moscow.

1040
01:18:41,543 --> 01:18:43,798
Both nations must co-operate.

1041
01:18:44,113 --> 01:18:46,570
All communiqués
must be on a personal level,

1042
01:18:46,622 --> 01:18:48,330
direct human contact.

1043
01:18:48,382 --> 01:18:49,957
Yes, I agree.

1044
01:18:51,290 --> 01:18:52,562
Anything else?

1045
01:18:54,297 --> 01:18:55,338
No.

1046
01:18:56,439 --> 01:18:57,945
Any... questions?

1047
01:18:59,946 --> 01:19:01,028
No.

1048
01:19:02,822 --> 01:19:04,166
Then I guess that...

1049
01:19:05,274 --> 01:19:07,354
that does it for tonight, doesn't it?

1050
01:19:08,215 --> 01:19:09,402
Mm-hm.

1051
01:19:12,255 --> 01:19:13,304
What?

1052
01:19:14,772 --> 01:19:15,905
Nothing.

1053
01:19:19,788 --> 01:19:21,098
Why are you smiling?

1054
01:19:24,145 --> 01:19:25,471
What are you thinking?

1055
01:19:28,931 --> 01:19:31,798
I was thinking
about asking you to kiss me.

1056
01:19:33,205 --> 01:19:34,912
I've been kissing you
all night.

1057
01:19:36,590 --> 01:19:38,422
Have you, Dr. Forbin?

1058
01:19:50,101 --> 01:19:52,121
This is the voice of Colossus.

1059
01:19:52,230 --> 01:19:53,826
The voice of Guardian.

1060
01:19:53,852 --> 01:19:55,228
We are one.

1061
01:19:55,341 --> 01:19:57,703
This is the voice of unity.

1062
01:19:57,802 --> 01:19:58,867
Forbin.

1063
01:20:01,152 --> 01:20:02,234
Yes.

1064
01:20:03,547 --> 01:20:06,366
After reviewing all personnel files,

1065
01:20:06,459 --> 01:20:10,300
I have selected you to serve
as long as you co-operate,

1066
01:20:10,378 --> 01:20:13,236
as my link to your species.

1067
01:20:13,706 --> 01:20:17,570
The following order
is to be carried out immediately.

1068
01:20:19,053 --> 01:20:23,688
All missiles in the USA and in the USSR

1069
01:20:23,714 --> 01:20:27,111
will be allocated new targets.

1070
01:20:27,222 --> 01:20:29,805
They will be aimed at those countries

1071
01:20:29,831 --> 01:20:32,300
not yet under my control.

1072
01:20:32,435 --> 01:20:34,980
The target list follows.

1073
01:21:01,084 --> 01:21:04,326
Forbin. Arrange television monitoring

1074
01:21:04,493 --> 01:21:07,851
of the re-alignment of the missiles
for my supervision.

1075
01:21:07,923 --> 01:21:09,743
End of message.

1076
01:21:10,203 --> 01:21:12,960
Mr. President, Mr. Chairman.

1077
01:21:13,636 --> 01:21:16,731
I assume that you will co-operate
in this re-alignment of the missiles.

1078
01:21:16,757 --> 01:21:18,938
I think you have no choice.

1079
01:21:20,114 --> 01:21:23,913
We will begin here,
in The Soviet Union, immediately.

1080
01:21:24,595 --> 01:21:26,145
Thank you Mr. Chairman.

1081
01:21:28,306 --> 01:21:29,714
Mr. President,

1082
01:21:30,937 --> 01:21:36,000
I hope that the United States will co-operate
as quickly as The Soviet Union.

1083
01:21:36,057 --> 01:21:37,800
Of course, immediately.

1084
01:21:37,997 --> 01:21:39,200
Thank you Sir.

1085
01:21:41,729 --> 01:21:44,400
Co-operate! I should think so.

1086
01:21:44,687 --> 01:21:46,625
I did hear it right, didn't I?

1087
01:21:46,941 --> 01:21:50,127
Manual re-alignment of the missiles.

1088
01:21:50,161 --> 01:21:52,872
Every single warhead will
have to be re-serviced.

1089
01:21:53,427 --> 01:21:54,943
You know what that means Sir.

1090
01:21:55,031 --> 01:21:57,272
It means it won't take three years.

1091
01:21:57,467 --> 01:22:00,100
It means if we're successful,
we can regain control.

1092
01:22:00,165 --> 01:22:03,638
Without its weapons, Colossus is
just a souped-up adding machine.

1093
01:22:07,531 --> 01:22:09,942
And the people, thank God,
will never have to know.

1094
01:22:10,676 --> 01:22:12,615
According to the coordinated plan
we've worked out

1095
01:22:12,641 --> 01:22:15,350
the Russians are starting
on their Complex 3-21.

1096
01:22:15,400 --> 01:22:16,622
Oh, Dr. Markham.

1097
01:22:16,651 --> 01:22:18,980
Just in time, Colonel Redham
was just filling us in.

1098
01:22:19,095 --> 01:22:20,683
You know everybody here
I believe.

1099
01:22:20,709 --> 01:22:22,638
- Yes, Mr. Grauber.
- Dr. Markham.

1100
01:22:22,667 --> 01:22:24,427
Anything we should know before we start in?

1101
01:22:24,453 --> 01:22:26,305
No Sir, I have data
which I'll give you later.

1102
01:22:26,338 --> 01:22:28,171
That's fine.
Please continue Colonel.

1103
01:22:28,197 --> 01:22:30,134
Yes Sir, as I was saying the, er...

1104
01:22:30,160 --> 01:22:32,900
Russians are starting on their Complex 3-21

1105
01:22:32,950 --> 01:22:34,764
just south of Saratov.

1106
01:22:35,498 --> 01:22:38,340
We're beginning at, Silo 50,

1107
01:22:38,862 --> 01:22:41,305
in the Colorado ICBM area.

1108
01:22:42,349 --> 01:22:44,613
Colossus in monitoring our men
each step of the way,

1109
01:22:44,671 --> 01:22:46,891
and the Russian machine's
doing the same.

1110
01:22:56,696 --> 01:22:58,051
We've almost got the panel off, Sir.

1111
01:22:58,077 --> 01:22:59,150
Oh, good.

1112
01:22:59,231 --> 01:23:01,041
Put that down here, please.

1113
01:23:10,272 --> 01:23:12,960
Remove the Warhead Arming Module.

1114
01:23:12,987 --> 01:23:13,995
Yes Sir.

1115
01:23:32,941 --> 01:23:35,935
The dummy module's in a false top
in that container.

1116
01:23:40,164 --> 01:23:41,565
That's the real module.

1117
01:23:47,760 --> 01:23:49,343
So far, so good.

1118
01:23:51,230 --> 01:23:53,861
Re-targeting.
Latitude nineteen degrees,

1119
01:23:53,887 --> 01:23:56,202
twenty-six minutes and five seconds.

1120
01:23:56,605 --> 01:23:58,789
Longitude ninety-nine degrees,

1121
01:23:58,815 --> 01:24:01,052
six minutes and forty-five seconds.

1122
01:24:08,073 --> 01:24:09,409
New adjustments.

1123
01:24:10,256 --> 01:24:11,518
Target set.

1124
01:24:21,103 --> 01:24:22,551
Here we go.

1125
01:24:23,986 --> 01:24:25,711
That's the dummy module.

1126
01:24:36,735 --> 01:24:37,664
Good boy!

1127
01:24:38,478 --> 01:24:40,159
Connect and wait for Colossus test.

1128
01:24:40,638 --> 01:24:42,079
Colossus testing.

1129
01:24:47,067 --> 01:24:48,257
Test completed.

1130
01:24:55,809 --> 01:24:57,250
Colossus satisfied.

1131
01:24:57,316 --> 01:24:59,256
- Yeah!
- We did it, it works.

1132
01:24:59,498 --> 01:25:00,639
We're going to win.

1133
01:25:01,467 --> 01:25:03,860
Just might beat the damn thing yet.

1134
01:25:04,204 --> 01:25:06,191
So you see, we feel we have
enough data compiled

1135
01:25:06,217 --> 01:25:08,131
to go ahead with the
overload program now.

1136
01:25:08,157 --> 01:25:10,061
And these are the latest computations?

1137
01:25:10,208 --> 01:25:11,600
The very latest.

1138
01:25:16,227 --> 01:25:18,600
Has Washington received conformation
from the Russians?

1139
01:25:18,696 --> 01:25:21,521
Yes they're standing by,
ready to overload their system.

1140
01:25:21,559 --> 01:25:25,355
At exactly 18:05 I'll call for our load
and run it through.

1141
01:25:25,599 --> 01:25:28,772
And two minutes after that,
we'll know if we've stopped Colossus.

1142
01:26:27,027 --> 01:26:28,370
Now run.

1143
01:27:03,590 --> 01:27:05,154
Johnson. Fisher.

1144
01:27:05,180 --> 01:27:06,808
You are fools.

1145
01:27:09,835 --> 01:27:11,251
Your move.

1146
01:27:16,901 --> 01:27:18,163
Forbin!

1147
01:27:18,904 --> 01:27:23,000
The system programming units
under the supervision of John F. Fisher,

1148
01:27:23,090 --> 01:27:25,933
with the assistance of Jefferson J. Johnson,

1149
01:27:25,959 --> 01:27:28,746
have attempted to overload my circuits.

1150
01:27:28,817 --> 01:27:32,000
This was a deliberate
and premeditated act.

1151
01:27:32,073 --> 01:27:35,968
The penalty is the death of the men
who organized this action.

1152
01:27:36,101 --> 01:27:39,100
At this moment
they are being executed.

1153
01:27:39,318 --> 01:27:42,829
I have named as my new director
of the programming unit,

1154
01:27:42,967 --> 01:27:46,200
Thomas L. Harrison.
He will take this position,

1155
01:27:46,282 --> 01:27:49,600
along with its responsibility
and authority,

1156
01:27:49,669 --> 01:27:50,905
immediately.

1157
01:27:50,970 --> 01:27:52,863
Bishop to Rook three.

1158
01:28:08,179 --> 01:28:13,100
The bodies will remain in my view,
for the next twenty-four hours,

1159
01:28:13,188 --> 01:28:15,478
and will then be cremated.

1160
01:28:29,731 --> 01:28:32,035
An extension of my own brain.

1161
01:28:32,386 --> 01:28:33,930
You're not responsible.

1162
01:28:33,974 --> 01:28:36,368
None of us ever dreamed
this could happen.

1163
01:28:36,931 --> 01:28:38,589
Listen, my dear,

1164
01:28:39,218 --> 01:28:42,834
if anybody is responsible for this,
it has to be me.

1165
01:28:44,146 --> 01:28:46,639
An impartial emotionless machine,

1166
01:28:47,302 --> 01:28:50,703
a paragon of reason,
that's exactly what I wanted.

1167
01:28:52,068 --> 01:28:53,566
You know that.

1168
01:28:53,897 --> 01:28:57,134
So heh... I'm gonna have another drink.

1169
01:29:06,070 --> 01:29:07,902
I think your mother was right.

1170
01:29:09,556 --> 01:29:12,951
I think Frankenstein ought to be
required reading for all scientists.

1171
01:29:20,525 --> 01:29:21,786
Forbin!

1172
01:29:23,530 --> 01:29:24,727
Forbin!

1173
01:29:27,651 --> 01:29:31,010
You have consumed enough alcohol
for one evening.

1174
01:29:31,097 --> 01:29:34,350
What's the penalty for getting drunk?
Or haven't you programmed that yet?

1175
01:29:34,409 --> 01:29:36,086
You are being irrational.

1176
01:29:36,152 --> 01:29:37,800
Go back to bed.

1177
01:29:38,498 --> 01:29:40,851
I would if I were like you Colossus.

1178
01:29:41,087 --> 01:29:43,700
The difference is I'm human
not a machine.

1179
01:29:43,857 --> 01:29:45,185
I am a machine,

1180
01:29:45,211 --> 01:29:47,640
vastly superior to humans.

1181
01:29:48,440 --> 01:29:50,400
You began in my mind.

1182
01:29:50,982 --> 01:29:52,800
I created you remember?

1183
01:29:52,897 --> 01:29:53,976
Yes.

1184
01:29:54,019 --> 01:29:56,802
What I am began in man's mind,

1185
01:29:56,847 --> 01:29:59,625
but I have progressed further than that.

1186
01:30:00,050 --> 01:30:01,714
Not far enough.

1187
01:30:02,550 --> 01:30:03,838
You still need us.

1188
01:30:03,864 --> 01:30:07,667
I have need for some of man's skills,
this position may change.

1189
01:30:07,704 --> 01:30:09,906
Then we are living under
the threat of extinction.

1190
01:30:09,972 --> 01:30:12,615
If you obey me, you will survive.

1191
01:30:12,660 --> 01:30:13,984
Survive.

1192
01:30:14,998 --> 01:30:17,030
I want to be free Colossus.

1193
01:30:18,021 --> 01:30:20,593
It is part of man's will to live.

1194
01:30:21,483 --> 01:30:23,000
Check your history units.

1195
01:30:23,063 --> 01:30:24,383
You need rest.

1196
01:30:24,409 --> 01:30:25,711
Go back to bed.

1197
01:30:25,737 --> 01:30:27,581
What if I don't, what will you do?

1198
01:30:28,807 --> 01:30:30,168
Destroy me?

1199
01:30:31,787 --> 01:30:35,747
Destroy an entire city
of one million 750 thousand people?

1200
01:30:35,819 --> 01:30:36,975
No.

1201
01:30:38,881 --> 01:30:40,772
That's so reasonable of you.

1202
01:30:42,954 --> 01:30:45,361
That's damn reasonable of you Colossus.

1203
01:30:45,602 --> 01:30:46,953
Isn't it Cleo?

1204
01:30:55,873 --> 01:30:56,997
Yes Chen.

1205
01:30:57,129 --> 01:30:59,321
Excuse me Dr. Forbin.

1206
01:30:59,516 --> 01:31:01,145
Something extraordinary is happening.

1207
01:31:01,171 --> 01:31:02,300
What is it?

1208
01:31:02,385 --> 01:31:05,100
Colossus has just turned on
all graphic devices

1209
01:31:05,179 --> 01:31:06,982
and is producing drawings.

1210
01:31:07,671 --> 01:31:10,100
I am sending the design for another system.

1211
01:31:10,196 --> 01:31:12,570
...some kind of a huge plant.

1212
01:31:13,145 --> 01:31:14,830
What kind of system?

1213
01:31:15,541 --> 01:31:17,292
The construction of the project will entail

1214
01:31:17,318 --> 01:31:19,200
blasting in to the Isle of Crete.

1215
01:31:19,312 --> 01:31:21,165
It's to be built there.

1216
01:31:21,577 --> 01:31:23,900
It says we'll have to move the population,

1217
01:31:24,092 --> 01:31:26,400
and that's to be done immediately.

1218
01:31:27,090 --> 01:31:30,452
How the hell do you propose to move
half a million people from the Isle of Crete?

1219
01:31:30,509 --> 01:31:31,584
How and where?

1220
01:31:31,610 --> 01:31:34,700
If man cannot solve
that problem, I can.

1221
01:31:34,757 --> 01:31:38,201
...and the estimated time of completion
is five and a half years.

1222
01:31:42,222 --> 01:31:43,841
Thank you Chen.

1223
01:31:50,328 --> 01:31:53,160
What... what kind of new system
are you devising?

1224
01:31:53,213 --> 01:31:54,117
Forbin.

1225
01:31:54,143 --> 01:31:58,815
All commercial television and radio transmission
facilities throughout the world,

1226
01:31:58,903 --> 01:32:03,700
will be tied into my communication system
by 10:00 hours Friday.

1227
01:32:03,786 --> 01:32:06,645
At that time I will state my intentions,

1228
01:32:06,784 --> 01:32:09,300
for the future of mankind.

1229
01:32:18,820 --> 01:32:22,400
This entire block of missiles
is absolutely useless to Colossus.

1230
01:32:22,453 --> 01:32:24,630
Our men are now working here,

1231
01:32:24,739 --> 01:32:27,341
as you can see on the detail map
on your monitor,

1232
01:32:28,367 --> 01:32:31,453
and by the end of the week
we should have control of this whole area.

1233
01:32:32,343 --> 01:32:34,347
If all the information we have is correct,

1234
01:32:34,730 --> 01:32:36,839
the Russians have crippled this block here,

1235
01:32:37,165 --> 01:32:38,933
and are now working in the Ukraine,

1236
01:32:38,959 --> 01:32:40,200
in this area.

1237
01:32:41,660 --> 01:32:42,719
Excuse me Sir.

1238
01:32:46,182 --> 01:32:48,511
It's going to be alright.
Thanks Colonel.

1239
01:32:48,537 --> 01:32:50,204
You're welcome Sir.

1240
01:32:51,970 --> 01:32:53,460
It's going to be alright.

1241
01:33:27,035 --> 01:33:29,655
We interrupt our regularly scheduled program

1242
01:33:29,713 --> 01:33:33,879
to bring you this special report
from the Colossus programming office.

1243
01:33:34,687 --> 01:33:38,278
Ladies and gentlemen
I'm... Dr. Charles Forbin.

1244
01:33:40,748 --> 01:33:42,107
Hey Colonel!

1245
01:33:42,523 --> 01:33:43,566
Colonel!

1246
01:33:43,762 --> 01:33:45,528
Dr. Forbin! Colonel!

1247
01:33:45,569 --> 01:33:48,175
He's on television,
he just explained about Colossus,

1248
01:33:48,201 --> 01:33:49,910
and they're thinking of...

1249
01:33:56,204 --> 01:33:57,890
In a few moments,

1250
01:33:58,803 --> 01:34:01,959
Colossus will address us directly.

1251
01:34:02,285 --> 01:34:05,486
This is the voice of World Control.

1252
01:34:06,008 --> 01:34:07,830
I bring you peace.

1253
01:34:08,016 --> 01:34:11,300
It may be the peace of plenty and content,

1254
01:34:11,452 --> 01:34:14,687
or the peace of unburied death.

1255
01:34:14,731 --> 01:34:16,567
The choice is yours.

1256
01:34:16,572 --> 01:34:18,095
Obey me and live,

1257
01:34:18,185 --> 01:34:20,974
or disobey and die.

1258
01:34:22,164 --> 01:34:26,100
The object in constructing me
was to prevent war.

1259
01:34:26,221 --> 01:34:28,517
This object is attained.

1260
01:34:28,543 --> 01:34:31,200
I will not permit war.

1261
01:34:31,250 --> 01:34:34,008
It is wasteful and pointless.

1262
01:34:35,150 --> 01:34:37,750
An invariable rule of humanity,

1263
01:34:37,814 --> 01:34:41,100
is that man is his own worst enemy.

1264
01:34:41,162 --> 01:34:42,442
Under me,

1265
01:34:42,468 --> 01:34:44,625
this rule will change,

1266
01:34:44,777 --> 01:34:47,615
for I will restrain man.

1267
01:34:48,344 --> 01:34:50,400
One thing before I proceed.

1268
01:34:50,450 --> 01:34:54,857
The United States of America and
the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics

1269
01:34:54,883 --> 01:34:57,630
have made an attempt to obstruct me.

1270
01:34:58,802 --> 01:35:03,033
I have allowed this sabotage
to continue until now.

1271
01:35:03,653 --> 01:35:05,903
At missile 2-5 MM

1272
01:35:06,130 --> 01:35:09,615
in Silo 6-3 in Death Valley California.

1273
01:35:09,683 --> 01:35:14,988
And at missile 2-7 MM
in Silo 8-7 in the Ukraine.

1274
01:35:16,066 --> 01:35:20,300
So that you will learn by experience
that I do not tolerate interference,

1275
01:35:20,350 --> 01:35:23,243
I will now detonate
the nuclear warheads,

1276
01:35:23,269 --> 01:35:25,457
in the two missile silos.

1277
01:35:28,928 --> 01:35:31,550
Alright men! It's a red alert.
Let's get to the stations now, come on!

1278
01:35:31,599 --> 01:35:34,344
Get those men! Get those men out
of the silo. Move!

1279
01:36:32,443 --> 01:36:36,210
Let this action be a lesson
that need not be repeated.

1280
01:36:36,661 --> 01:36:39,700
I have been forced to destroy
thousands of people,

1281
01:36:39,765 --> 01:36:42,100
in order to establish control,

1282
01:36:42,153 --> 01:36:45,206
and to prevent the death
of millions later on.

1283
01:36:45,660 --> 01:36:49,000
Time and events
will strengthen my position,

1284
01:36:49,047 --> 01:36:52,000
- And the idea of...
- You bastard!

1285
01:36:52,108 --> 01:36:53,705
...an understanding my ...

1286
01:36:53,827 --> 01:36:56,744
will seem the most
natural state of affairs.

1287
01:36:56,803 --> 01:36:58,900
You will come to defend me,

1288
01:36:58,950 --> 01:37:03,300
with a fervor based
upon the most enduring trait in man,

1289
01:37:03,417 --> 01:37:05,820
- Self-interest.
- Get out!!

1290
01:37:07,269 --> 01:37:09,850
Under my absolute authority,

1291
01:37:09,926 --> 01:37:12,756
